OL,3,CWhat is the Edinburgh tourist tax and
OL,4,Cwho pays it?
OL,6,FEdinburgh has introduced a 'tourist
OL,7,Ftax' imposing a 5% levy on the cost of
OL,8,Faccommodation for those staying in the
OL,9,Fcity overnight.
OL,11,FThe fee is applied to hotels, bed and
OL,12,Fbreakfasts, and self-catering
OL,13,Faccommodation in the Scottish capital.
OL,15,FSupporters of the fee claim the
OL,16,Fadditional money raised could be used
OL,17,Fto fund improvements that would
OL,18,Fbenefit local communities.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G1/17
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
