OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F304A1784897315
OL,3,CWhat is the Edinburgh tourist tax and
OL,4,Cwho pays it?
OL,6,FOthers fear it may put people off
OL,7,Fvisiting altogether, in what can
OL,8,Falready be an expensive city to visit.
OL,10,FBut how much could you be forced to
OL,11,Fpay and is this something we are
OL,12,Flikely to see more of?
OL,14,FWhat is the Edinburgh tourist tax?
OL,16,FThe visitor levy being applied to
OL,17,Fovernight stays in Edinburgh has been
OL,18,Fset at 5% of the total cost of your
OL,19,Faccommodation, capped at five nights.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G2/17
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
