CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F304A1784897315
OL,3,CWhat is the Edinburgh tourist tax and
OL,4,Cwho pays it?
OL,6,FThe fee is added to the bill when you
OL,7,Fpay for your accommodation before
OL,8,Fbeing passed to the council.
OL,10,FA five-night stay costing #1,000 would
OL,11,Fnow cost #1050, with the #50 levy
OL,12,Fbeing added to the final bill. Staying
OL,13,Fin the same accommodation for 10
OL,14,Fnights at a cost of #2,000 would still
OL,15,Fonly see a #50 levy added (5% of the
OL,16,Ffirst five nights).
OL,18,FThe Scottish government passed the
OL,19,Flegislation to enact these levies in
OL,20,F2024 in the Visitor Levy (Scotland)
OL,21,FBill.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G3/17
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
