OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F304A1784897315
OL,3,CWhat is the Edinburgh tourist tax and
OL,4,Cwho pays it?
OL,6,FEdinburgh Council voted in favour of
OL,7,Fenacting a tax in January last year.
OL,9,FWho pays the tax?
OL,11,FEveryone visiting Edinburgh and paying
OL,12,Ffor accommodation to stay overnight
OL,13,Fpays the levy.
OL,15,FThis includes those visiting from
OL,16,Fabroad and UK citizens, including
OL,17,FScots living elsewhere in Scotland.
OL,19,FThose only visiting for a day trip do
OL,20,Fnot need to pay, as the charge is only
OL,21,Fadded to accommodation costs.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G4/17
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,305,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30405
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F304A1784897315
OL,3,CWhat is the Edinburgh tourist tax and
OL,4,Cwho pays it?
OL,6,FHotels, bed and breakfasts, holiday
OL,7,Flets like AirBnBs, student lets not
OL,8,Fbeing used by students outside of term
OL,9,Ftime, caravans and campsites, and
OL,10,Fboats moored in one location will all
OL,11,Fsee the charge added.
OL,13,FAugust is traditionally one of the
OL,14,Fbusiest times of the year for
OL,15,FEdinburgh, with the Fringe Festival,
OL,16,Fbook festival, film festival, and TV
OL,17,Ffestival all taking place in the month.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G5/17
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
