OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F304A1784897315
OL,3,CWhat is the Edinburgh tourist tax and
OL,4,Cwho pays it?
OL,6,FThe new charge will be in place before
OL,7,Fthen, meaning those staying in the
OL,8,Fcity for any of these events will be
OL,9,Fhit with the tax.
OL,11,FThe levy applies to anyone who booked
OL,12,Ftheir stay after October 1, 2025,
OL,13,Fmeaning those who had already budgeted
OL,14,Ffor their trip may now face the extra
OL,15,Fcharge.
OL,17,FWhat will the money be used for?
OL,19,FThe council estimates the visitor levy
OL,20,Fcould raise as much as #50 million by
OL,21,Fthe end of the 2028/29 tax year.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G6/17
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
