OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F304A1784897315
OL,3,CWhat is the Edinburgh tourist tax and
OL,4,Cwho pays it?
OL,6,FLaws mean the money can only be used
OL,7,Fto reinvest in local services and
OL,8,Ffacilities that will directly benefit
OL,9,Fthe community.
OL,11,FSeveral funding projects have already
OL,12,Fbeen announced as a result of this
OL,13,Fcharge.
OL,15,FLeith Theatre is set to receive #5
OL,16,Fmillion to fund its restoration, with
OL,17,Fanother #3 million being used to fund
OL,18,Fthe conversion of the Old Royal High
OL,19,FSchool into a national music centre.
OL,21,FHow have people reacted?
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G7/17
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
