OL,3,CWhat is the Edinburgh tourist tax and
OL,4,Cwho pays it?
OL,6,FBusinesses which rely on tourism have
OL,7,Fraised concerns that increased costs
OL,8,Ffor visitors may make the city a less
OL,9,Fappealing place to stay.
OL,11,FMarc Crothall MBE, Chief Executive of
OL,12,Fthe Scottish Tourism Alliance, said:
OL,13,F"A visitor levy has always threatened
OL,14,FScotland's price competitiveness and
OL,15,Frisks creating a tipping point that
OL,16,Fmany visitors will be unwilling to
OL,17,Fpay, further impacting the declining
OL,18,Fdomestic market."
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G8/17
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
