OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F304A1784897315
OL,3,CWhat is the Edinburgh tourist tax and
OL,4,Cwho pays it?
OL,6,FVoices from within the performing arts
OL,7,Fcommunity have also raised concerns
OL,8,Fabout the rising cost of bringing
OL,9,Fshows and performances to Edinburgh,
OL,10,Fespecially ahead of August festival
OL,11,Fseason.
OL,13,FSteven Roth, the executive director of
OL,14,FScottish Ballet, said: "The economics
OL,15,Fof touring to Edinburgh are fast
OL,16,Fbecoming unsustainable."
OL,26,@vD@XOUxD@XO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G9/17
