OL,3,CWhat is the Edinburgh tourist tax and
OL,4,Cwho pays it?
OL,6,FThe Glasgow-based dance company said
OL,7,Fits bill for housing its touring
OL,8,Fcompany of up to 150 performers and
OL,9,Fcrew in the capital had risen by 72%
OL,10,Fbetween December 2019 and December
OL,11,F2025 ` and now tops more than #200,000.
OL,13,FTo help with the costs, it has called
OL,14,Fon Edinburgh City Council to introduce
OL,15,Fan exemption or relief scheme to the
OL,16,Fnew visitor levy for Scotland's
OL,17,Fnational performing arts companies `
OL,18,Ffour out of five of which are based in
OL,19,FGlasgow.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G10/17
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
