OL,3,CWhat is the Edinburgh tourist tax and
OL,4,Cwho pays it?
OL,6,FSubscribe free to our weekly
OL,7,Fnewsletter for exclusive and original
OL,8,Fcoverage from ITV News. Direct to your
OL,9,Finbox every Friday morning.
OL,11,FBut City Council leader Jane Meagher
OL,12,Fsaid the tax would have little impact
OL,13,Fon visitor numbers.
OL,15,F"We've done a lot of research into the
OL,16,Feffect of visitor levies in other
OL,17,Fcities and other countries and there's
OL,18,Fno discernible change to visitor
OL,19,Fnumbers.
OL,26,@wD@AOU
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G11/17
