OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F304A1784897315
OL,3,CWhat is the Edinburgh tourist tax and
OL,4,Cwho pays it?
OL,6,F"And I anticipate that, because the
OL,7,Fcity will be able to offer much more,
OL,8,Fincluding access to the many hidden
OL,9,Fgems in this city, that we'll be able
OL,10,Fto attract even more visitors.
OL,12,F"We've got two world heritage centres,
OL,13,Fnot just one, we've got two, we've got
OL,14,Fcastles galore. We've got so much for
OL,15,Fpeople to see."
OL,17,FShe added that rising costs are mainly
OL,18,Fdue to "hotel costs" which is not
OL,19,Fsomething the council "has any control
OL,20,Fover".
