OL,3,CWhat is the Edinburgh tourist tax and
OL,4,Cwho pays it?
OL,6,FCould we see more of these taxes in
OL,7,Fother UK cities?
OL,9,FThe move by Edinburgh Council brings
OL,10,Fthe Scottish capital in line with
OL,11,FEuropean destinations including
OL,12,FAmsterdam, Paris, and Rome.
OL,14,FIn Scotland, Glasgow, Aberdeen,
OL,15,FStirling and West Dunbartonshire,
OL,16,Fcouncils have already approved their
OL,17,Fown levies.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G13/17
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
