OL,3,CWhat is the Edinburgh tourist tax and
OL,4,Cwho pays it?
OL,6,FBoth Manchester and Liverpool already
OL,7,Fhave their own versions of the visitor
OL,8,Flevy in place, though these exclude
OL,9,Fprivate rentals like AirBnBs.
OL,11,FIn both these instances, hotels in a
OL,12,Fdefined zone held ballots to vote to
OL,13,Fimpose the charges as local
OL,14,Fauthorities lacked the legal powers to
OL,15,Fdo so.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G14/17
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
