OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F304A1784897315
OL,3,CWhat is the Edinburgh tourist tax and
OL,4,Cwho pays it?
OL,6,FThis could soon change though, as the
OL,7,Fgovernment included legislation in the
OL,8,F2026 King's Speech to give local
OL,9,Fauthorities in England the power to
OL,10,Fimpose their own mandatory charges,
OL,11,Fbringing England in line with Scotland
OL,12,Fand Wales.
OL,14,FResponding at the time, Allen Simpson,
OL,15,Fchief executive of UKHospitality,
OL,16,Fsaid: "The government has confirmed it
OL,17,Fwill legislate to make family holidays
OL,18,Fmore expensive during a cost-of-living
OL,19,Fcrisis.
OL,26,@xD@GOU
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G15/17
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
