PN,30416
SC,0016
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F304A1784897315
OL,3,CWhat is the Edinburgh tourist tax and
OL,4,Cwho pays it?
OL,6,F"It's a shocking U-turn after it told
OL,7,Fboth the House of Commons and
OL,8,FUKHospitality that it would not
OL,9,Fimplement a holiday tax.
OL,11,F"The facts are simple. A holiday tax
OL,12,Fwill increase the cost of a staycation
OL,13,Ffor Brits, it will hit lower-income
OL,14,Ffamilies hardest, it will lose the
OL,15,FTreasury money, and it will cost
OL,16,F33,000 jobs."
OL,18,FSome regional leaders welcomed the
OL,19,Fannouncement however.
OL,26,@nD@AOUsD@AOU
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G16/17
