OL,3,CWhat is the Edinburgh tourist tax and
OL,4,Cwho pays it?
OL,6,FLondon Mayor Sir Sadiq Khan said
OL,7,F"extra funding will directly support
OL,8,FLondon's economy", while Liverpool
OL,9,FCity Region Mayor Steve Rotheram said
OL,10,Fa "modest levy is money that would
OL,11,Fstay local".
